    "monster5517": "<h1 class=monster>Nganga<br><span class=type>Medium natural humanoid, human</span><br><span class=level>Level 11 Artillery<span class=xp> XP 600</span></span></h1><table class=bodytable><tr><td><b>HP</b> 90; <b>Bloodied</b> 45<td class=rightalign><b>Initiative</b> +7<tr><td><b>AC</b> 23, <b>Fortitude</b> 23, <b>Reflex</b> 22, <b>Will</b> 24<td class=rightalign><b>Perception</b>+9<tr><td><b>Speed</b> 6<td class=rightalign><tr><td colspan=2></table><h2>Standard Actions</h2><p class='flavor alt'>(⚔) <b>Spirit Rattle</b> (weapon) ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Attack:</i> Melee 1 (one creature); +16 vs. AC</p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Hit:</i> 2d10 + 4 damage.</p><p class='flavor alt'>(➶) <b>Ghost Lance</b> (necrotic) ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Attack:</i> Ranged 20 (one creature); +16 vs. Fortitude</p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Hit:</i> 4d6 + 5 necrotic damage.</p><p class='flavor alt'>➶ <b>Spectral Jaws</b> (force) ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Attack:</i> Ranged 12 (one creature); +18 vs. AC</p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Hit:</i> 2d8 + 10 force damage, and the target is immobilized (save ends).</p><p class='flavor alt'>ᗕ <b>Devil Mask</b> (fear, psychic) ✦ <b>Encounter</b></p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Attack:</i> Close blast 3 (creatures in the blast); +16 vs. Will</p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Hit:</i> 3d8 + 5 psychic damage, and the nganga pushes the target 3 squares. At the start of each of the target's subsequent turns, the nganga can push the target 3 squares as a free action (save ends).</p><h2>Minor Actions</h2><p class='flavor alt'> <b>Curse of the Oba</b> ✦ <b>Encounter</b></p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Effect:</i> One creature within 15 squares of the nganga is cursed until the end of the encounter. When the nganga deals damage with a melee or a ranged attack to a target other than the cursed creature, the cursed creature takes an equal amount of damage.</p><p class='flavor alt'><b>Skills</b> Arcana +13, Insight +14, Stealth +12<br> <b>Str</b> 15 (+7)                <b>Dex</b> 15 (+7)                <b>Wis</b> 18 (+9)<br><b>Con</b> 18 (+9)                <b>Int</b> 17 (+8)                <b>Cha</b> 21 (+10)</p><p class=flavor><b>Alignment</b> Evil       <b> Languages</b> Common, Primordial<br><b>Equipment</b>: spirit rattle, drums, mask, necklace</p><p class=publishedIn>Published in Dark Sun Creature Catalog, page(s) 113.</p>",
